div.p:
If Miss Vervain wanted to turn the talk upon Don Ippolito, Ferris by no means did;
                  he had had enough of that subject yesterday; he got as lightly away from it as he
                  could.

The old wretch set up a pitiful whimper, and tried to possess herself of his hand;
                  she kissed his coat-sleeve instead. "That you will return with me," she besought
                  him.
